=\"dot\">•</span>门      票：</strong>\n                                行程中注明需要另行支付的自费景点（黛螺顶8元/人）。\n                            </p>\n                            \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                            <p class=\"item-label\">\n                                <strong><span class=\"dot\">•</span>其      他：</strong>\n                                自行安排往返以及景区内用车安排，行程中不含全程餐费。\n                            </p>\n                            \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                            <p class=\"item-label\">\n                                <strong><span class=\"dot\">•</span>补      充：</strong>\n                                酒店内洗衣、理发、电话、传真、收费电视、饮品、烟酒等个人消费。；当地参加的自费以及以上\"费用包含\"中不包含的其它项目。\n                            </p>\n                            \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                            <p class=\"item-label\">\n                                <strong><span class=\"dot\">•</span>旅游意外险：</strong>\n                                旅游人身意外保险\n                            </p>\n                            \n                        \n                    \n                </div>\n            \n\n            \n            \n\n            \n            \n                <div class=\"section-box-title\">\n                    <h3>活动推荐</h3>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"section-box-content\">\n                    <table class=\"detail-upgrade-activity\">\n                        <thead>\n                            <tr>\n                                <th class=\"col-1\">活动名称</th>\n                                <th class=\"col-2\">参考价格</th>\n                                <th class=\"col-1\">详细说明</th>\n                                <th class=\"col-3\">备注</th>\n                            </tr>\n                        </thead>\n           