 \n            \n                <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd1-m1-s0\">\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <ul class=\"detail-journey-list\">\n                            \n                                <li><i class=\"icon detail-journey-icon-clock\"></i>游玩时长：约3小时30分钟</li>\n                            \n                        </ul>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-desc\">（参考时间）早餐后，出发前往参观游览【天目湖山水园】（挂牌价180元/人，含游船，费用已含）；天目湖山水园，四面群山枕水、碧波荡漾，湖中岛屿散落、湖岸曲折通幽，以山绕水、水映山而取胜。景区植被覆盖率达85%以上，拥有植物200多种，接触自然，领略自然风光，体验乡土气息，天目湖山水园己成为华东地区美丽的后花园。该景区自然和人文景观相结合：湖里山、乡村田园岛、海洋世界、绣球岛――品味天目湖＂茶香水甜＂之**处。</div>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"detail-journey-photos\">\n        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\">\n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"J_ViewDetail detail-journey-photo-item detail-journey-photo-item-clickable\" data-id=\"d1-m1-s0\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\">\n                            \n                                <img src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G4/M00/3B/53/Cii-VVm19KKILG21ABiDjnn9EkwAABEPQNkhFkAGIOm881_w640_h480_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G4/M00/3B/53/Cii-VVm19KKILG21ABiDjnn9EkwAABEPQNkhFkAGIOm881_w640_h480_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            \n\n                            \n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-mask\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-title\">天目湖山水园</div>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                \n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"J_ViewDetail detail-journey-photo-item detail-journey-photo-item-clickabl