ail-journey-seprate\"></div>\n        \n    </div>\n\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m1\">\n        \n        <div class=\"detail-journey-title\">\n            \n            <i class=\"icon detail-journey-label-note\"></i>\n            \n            \n            \n            \n                \n                温馨提示\n            \n            \n        </div>\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n            <div class=\"detail-journey-desc\"><p><font color=\"#ff9702\">●今日拍点：[李家山全景、黄河画廊&nbsp;]</font></p><p>①出行前一天，导游会与您电话联系，确认集合细节，请手机保持通畅。<br></p><p>②因散客拼团，早上集合可能会存在等待情况，敬请谅解。</p></div>\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n\n\n\n\n\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n            <div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\"></div>\n        \n    </div>\n\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m2\">\n        \n        <div class=\"detail-journey-title\">\n            \n            <i class=\"icon detail-journey-label-spot\"></i>\n            \n            \n            \n            \n                景点 · 【碛口古镇】（黄河古渡口）\n                \n                         \n                  \n            \n            \n        </div>\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n\n\n\n\n\n        \n        \n            \n                <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m2-s0\">\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <ul class=\"detail-journey-list\">\n                            \n                        </ul>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-desc\"><p>中国历史文化名镇，黄河由北而来，湫水从东而至，卧虎山横亘镇北，黑龙庙雄峙河东，山环水抱，阴阳交会，山的气势，河的雄浑，形成了“虎啸黄河，龙吟碛口”的壮丽图景。</p></div>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"detail-journey-photos\">\n        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\">\n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\">\n                            \n                                <img src=\"//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder-4x3.png\" data-src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G4/M00/C3/67/Cii_J1xxLM-IAlqcAAnP_rO49fYAAEFzgKIu4EACdAW711_w640_h480_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            \n\n                            \n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-mask\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-title\">碛口古镇</div>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                \n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\">\n                            \n                                <img src=\"//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder-4x3.png\" data-src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G5/M00/A5/75/Cii-slxxLOeILfXhAAjBNepj-_UAAUDAgHCyAoACMFN393_w640_h480_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            \n\n                            \n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-mask\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-title\">碛口古镇</div>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                        <div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\"></div>\n                    \n                \n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n\n                </div>\n            \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n            <div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\"></div>\n        \n    </div>\n\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m3\">\n        \n        <div class=\"detail-journey-title\">\n            \n            <i class=\"icon detail-journey-label-spot\"></i>\n            \n            \n            \n            \n                景点 · 【李家山村】（历史文化名村）    \n                \n                         \n                  \n            \n            \n        </div>\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n\n\n\n\n\n        \n        \n            \n                <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m3-s0\">\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <ul class=\"detail-journey-list\">\n                            \n                        </ul>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-desc\"><p>著名画家吴冠中一生的三大发现之一，隐于大山深处，空灵幽雅，从外部看像一座荒凉的汉墓，一进去是很古老讲究的窑洞，古村相对封闭，像与世隔绝的桃花源。</p></div>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"detail-journey-photos\">\n        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\">\n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\">\n                            \n                                <img src=\"//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder-4x3.png\" data-src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G5/M00/A5/7A/Cii-tFxxLiiIC2j-AAu7wxPc86UAAUDAwNd1RYAC7vb072_w640_h480_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            \n\n                            \n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-mask\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-titl