              <ul class=\"detail-journey-list\">\n                            \n                        </ul>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-desc\">位于临县南端湫水河入口处的碛口镇卧虎山上，整体建筑严谨合理，左右对称，奇伟壮观。仰观庙宇叠于石崖之险，雕梁画栋，古朴典雅，无不使人悦目赏心。倚庙廊俯而环视，只见黄河滔滔，批水潺潺，古老的碛口镇尽收眼底。</div>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"detail-journey-photos\">\n        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\">\n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\">\n                            \n                                <img src=\"//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder-4x3.png\" data-src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G4/M00/C3/69/Cii_J1xxMQaIHOSdAAkqeccYe4QAAEF0QNHW8oACSqR895_w640_h480_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            \n\n                            \n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-mask\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-title\">黑龙庙</div>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                \n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\">\n                            \n                                <img src=\"//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder-4x3.png\" data-src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com//fb2/t1/G2/M00/05/9E/Cii-TFiZblyIdSnmAAlK1xM6AiQAAHB3gF91pUACUrv883_w640_h480_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            \n\n                            \n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-mask\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-title\">黑龙庙</div>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                        <div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\"></div>\n                    \n                \n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n\n                </div>\n            \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n            <div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\"></div>\n        \n    </div>\n\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m5\">\n        \n        <div class=\"detail-journey-title\">\n            \n            <i class=\"icon detail-journey-label-spot\"></i>\n            \n            \n            \n            \n                景点 · 【黄河画廊】（大自然馈赠）\n                \n                         \n                  \n            \n            \n        </div>\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n\n\n\n\n\n        \n        \n            \n                <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m5-s0\">\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <ul class=\"detail-journey-list\">\n                            \n                        </ul>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-desc\">黄河岸边石壁上，大大小小无规律的分布着各种形状的沟壑和纹理，像一幅幅精美的画卷。这一幅幅精美绝伦的壮丽图画，有的如行云流水，有的似山水人物，有的甚至像极了繁体中国汉字的“福、禄、寿”字。这些天然石雕，鬼斧神工，是几十万年前黄河水冲刷出来的杰作。</div>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"detail-journey-photos\">\n        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\">\n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\">\n                            \n                    