INSERT INTO `i_traveldetails` VALUES (47, '<天津汽车往返1日游>北京五环内可接，含午餐，乘船出海，意式风情街，瓷房子，古文化街，滨海新区，特色之旅一日游', 'images/tianjin.jpg', NULL, NULL, 47, NULL, NULL, 122.00, 59.00, '<img src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G5/M00/17/66/Cii-slubG6aIPVE7ADOQFhxjOrUAANrmALwKbIAM5Au488_w1024_h0_c0_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G5/M00/17/66/Cii-slubG6aIPVE7ADOQFhxjOrUAANrmALwKbIAM5Au488_w1024_h0_c0_t0.jpg\">', '<div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0\">\n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-head\">\n                        <i class=\"icon detail-journey-day\">D1</i>\n                        <strong>第1天</strong>\n\n                        \n                            <strong>北京</strong>\n                            \n                                \n                                    <i class=\"icon detail-journey-transport-car\"></i>\n                                \n                                <strong>天津</strong>\n                            \n                        \n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-seprate-solid\"></div>\n\n                    \n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m0\">\n        \n        <div class=\"detail-journey-title\">\n            \n            <i class=\"icon detail-journey-label-transport\"></i>\n            \n            \n            \n            \n                \n                \n                    <strong>北京</strong>\n                \n                \n                    \n                        <i class=\"icon detail-journey-transport-car\"></i>\n                    \n                    <strong>天津</strong>\n                \n            \n            \n        </div>\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n            <div class=\"detail-journey-desc\">北京五环内接客人，5:30-6:00到酒店或指定地点集合接客人，而后乘大巴到天津！</div>\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n\n\n\n\n\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n            <div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\"></div>\n        \n    </div>\n\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m1\">\n        \n        <div class=\"detail-journey-title\">\n            \n            <i class=\"icon detail-journey-label-spot\"></i>\n            \n            \n                <i class=\"detail-journey-time\">09:00</i>\n            \n            \n            \n                景点 · 海河桥\n                \n                         \n                  \n            \n            \n        </div>\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n\n\n\n\n\n        \n        \n            \n                <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m1-s0\">\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <ul class=\"detail-journey-list\">\n                            \n                        </ul>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-desc\"><p>到达天津市区，外观海河大桥、天津之眼摩天轮；天津被誉为“九河下稍”，海河是天津的“母亲河”。海河像是天津这座城市的绸带，而海河上的一座座桥梁则是绸带上镶嵌的珍珠，成为城市中地标性质的亮点所在。这些大桥或古老或年轻，充满租界时代欧式风情，每一座桥上都铭刻着岁月的痕迹。如天津浮桥，建于清康熙五十四年，曾是天津的八景之一。清光绪十四年，即1888年，天津悬臂式开启桥在南运河上建成，取名金华桥。中国著名桥梁专家茅以升曾经说过：“几乎全国的开合桥都集中在天津。</p><p><br></p></div>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"detail-journey-photos\">\n        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\">\n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\">\n                            \n                                <img src=\"//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder-4x3.png\" data-src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com//fb2/t1/G3/M00/38/48/Cii_JVllgrWIO0HkAEBSWeKrlCMAADVkwE7ZvwAQFJx057_w640_h480_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            \n\n                            \n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-mask\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-title\">天津海河大沽桥</div>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                \n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\">\n                            \n                                <img src=\"//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder-4x3.png\" data-src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com//fb2/t1/G3/M00/37/1A/Cii_JVlkocOIIZxSAEFgvJmly0kAADQcgEfgfwAQWDU657_w640_h480_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            \n\n                            \n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-mask\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-title\">天津海河风光</div>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                        <div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\"></div>\n                    \n                \n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n\n                </div>\n            \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n            <div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\"></div>\n        \n    </div>\n\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m2\">\n        \n        <div class=\"detail-journey-title\">\n            \n            <i class=\"icon detail-journey-label-spot\"></i>\n            \n            \n                <i class=\"detail-journey-time\">09:30</i>\n            \n            \n            \n                景点 · 天津意式风情区\n                \n                         \n                  \n            \n            \n        </div>\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n\n\n\n\n\n        \n        \n            \n                <div class=\"J_JourneyItemd0-m2-s0\">\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <ul class=\"detail-journey-list\">\n                            \n                        </ul>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                    \n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-desc\"><p>天津意式风情街紧挨着海河，有大量意大利风情建筑。这里的意大利风格的小洋楼成群，让你感觉彷佛置身于马可波罗故乡的古老小镇，温馨又随和。 街区中心喷水柱的圆形广场的名字，就叫马可·波罗。在意大利老租界里，还有梁启超的饮冰室、曹禺故居、李叔同故居、袁世凯及冯国璋的府邸等。</p></div>\n                    \n                    \n                    \n\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"detail-journey-photos\">\n        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\">\n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\">\n                            \n                                <img src=\"//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder-4x3.png\" data-src=\"//m.tuniucdn.com//fb2/t1/G3/M00/01/4A/Cii_JVlAruSITQjOAKuWydpmOGwAAAMugMDyZEAq5bh588_w640_h480_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                            \n\n                            \n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-mask\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-title\">意式风情街</div>\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                \n            \n                \n                    <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\">\n                        <div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\">\n                            \n                                <img src=\"//img1.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/c